2007 release. Filmed and recorded at Leverkusen Jazztage, Germany in November, 2006. Di Meola rediscovers his love of the electric guitar without denying newer influences. The result is a balancing act between volcanic electronic ecstacy and emotionally moving sound excursions, between fervent improvisations and intimate conversations,
 including many Al Di Meola compositions and 5 Astor Piazzolla tunes.
